[DhtmlXQ_comment11]And the opening formation is basically defined.||Red uses the Central Cannon with 7th Filed Horse while Black counters with the Screen Horse Defense.||According to my annotated book, GM Lv Qin and GM Hong Zhi had been studying this opening ferociously in preparation for the Asean games.||They had created many flying daggers...[/DhtmlXQ_comment11]
[DhtmlXQ_comment14]Master Sun is very familiar with pushing the cannon forward for this opening variation and is one of his "secret" weapons.||Master Sun decides to play something familiar against the young GM. It is also an opening that he has studied ferouciously.[/DhtmlXQ_comment14]
